Jennifer Lopez, 52, stepped out with Ben Affleck, 49, and his 10-year-old son Samuel to browse luxury cars at a Rolls Royce dealership in Beverly Hills on Saturday.J.Lo was pictured holding hands with Samuel and later laughed and hugged with her fiancéThe trio cut a casual figure with Jennifer looking stunning as ever in flared jeans, white trainers, a white bodysuit and a large Christian Dior bag.She accessorised with her statement hooped earrings, sunglasses and wore her long hair in a low ponytail.The outing comes a week after Samuel, who Ben shares with Jennifer Garner, accidentally bumped his dad’s Lamborghini into a BMW as he sat in the front seat while the engine was still on.